4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential skills in JavaScript and Python over a 16-week program (plus 2 weeks for project presentation). Classes run three times a week with a low student-to-teacher ratio of 7:1. No prior coding experience is required, and students can choose English or Spanish for their instruction. The curriculum emphasizes web development, algorithm scripting, and the use of APIs to create robust applications. Upon completion, graduates receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop